query:
SELECT 
  er.employeeId,
  e.name as employee_name,
  e.code as employee_code,
  SUM(er.total) as weekly_revenue,
  dr.date
FROM employeeRevenues er
JOIN dailyRevenues dr ON er.dailyRevenueId = dr.id
JOIN employees e ON er.employeeId = e.id
JOIN branches b ON dr.branchId = b.id
WHERE b.name LIKE '%طويق%'
AND dr.date BETWEEN '2026-01-15' AND '2026-01-21'
GROUP BY er.employeeId, e.name, e.code, dr.date
ORDER BY dr.date, e.name;
